The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 BCCI SGM on June 1

New Delhi: A special general meeting (SGM) of the BCCI will be held in Mumbai on June 1 to decide on matters relating to the 2011 World Cup and constitutional review. 

The meeting will take decisions relating to conduct and organisation of the 2011 World Cup, secretary Niranjan Shah said in a press release. 

A decision on amendment of rules and regulations as recommended by constitution review committee will also be taken. (PTI) 




